---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="RoboMission - WRO 2026 Mie">
    <div class="relative w-full overflow-x-hidden min-h-screen bg-slate-50">
        <!-- Hero -->
        <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 px-4 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none">
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-blue-100 rounded-full blur-3xl transform translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"
                >
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl relative z-10 text-center">
                <span
                    class="text-blue-600 font-bold tracking-wider text-sm ring-1 ring-blue-200 bg-blue-50 px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 inline-block uppercase"
                >
                    The Classic Challenge
                </span>
                <h1
                    class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
                >
                    RoboMission
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
                >
                    チームは自律型ロボットを設計・構築・プログラミングし、フィールド上の特定の課題を解決します。スピード、正確性、そしてエンジニアリングの精度が鍵となります。
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Content -->
        <main class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-12 space-y-24">
            <!-- Categories Grid -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Elementary -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group shadow-sm"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-blue-500 font-bold text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                    >
                        E
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">
                        Elementary
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        初心者や低学年向け。基本的な移動とオブジェクト操作に焦点を当てています。
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-500 mb-8">
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <span
                                class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"
                            ></span>対象年齢: 8-12歳
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <span
                                class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"
                            ></span>基本センサー制御
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a
                        href="https://wro-association.org/wp-content/uploads/WRO-2026-RoboMission-Elementary-Game-Rules.pdf"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="block w-full text-center py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-900 hover:text-white transition-all font-medium text-sm text-slate-700"
                    >
                        ルールをダウンロード
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- Junior -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:border-purple-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group shadow-sm"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-purple-500 font-bold text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                    >
                        J
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">
                        Junior
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        より複雑なロジック、色識別、信頼性が求められる中級レベルの課題。
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-500 mb-8">
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <span
                                class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mr-2"
                            ></span>対象年齢: 11-15歳
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <span
                                class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mr-2"
                            ></span>高度なロジック
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a
                        href="https://wro-association.org/wp-content/uploads/WRO-2026-RoboMission-Junior-Game-Rules.pdf"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="block w-full text-center py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-900 hover:text-white transition-all font-medium text-sm text-slate-700"
                    >
                        ルールをダウンロード
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- Senior -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:border-amber-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group shadow-sm"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-amber-500 font-bold text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                    >
                        S
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">
                        Senior
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        究極の挑戦。複雑な経路探索、オブジェクト管理、そしてハイスピードな動作が求められます。
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-500 mb-8">
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <span
                                class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-amber-500 rounded-full mr-2"
                            ></span>対象年齢: 14-19歳
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <span
                                class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-amber-500 rounded-full mr-2"
                            ></span>複雑なエンジニアリング
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a
                        href="https://wro-association.org/wp-content/uploads/WRO-2026-RoboMission-Senior-Game-Rules.pdf"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="block w-full text-center py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-900 hover:text-white transition-all font-medium text-sm text-slate-700"
                    >
                        ルールをダウンロード
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- General Resources -->
            <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-slate-900">
                    General Resources
                </h2>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <a
                        href="https://wro-association.org/wp-content/uploads/WRO-2026-RoboMission-General-Rules.pdf"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="flex items-center p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-md transition-all group"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="mr-4 text-slate-400 group-hover:text-blue-500"
                        >
                            <svg
                                width="24"
                                height="24"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                ><path
                                    d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"
                                ></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"
                                ></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"
                                ></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"
                                ></line><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"
                                ></polyline></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold mb-1 text-slate-900">
                                General Rules
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
                                全年齢グループ共通の公式規定。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a
                        href="https://wro-association.org/wp-content/uploads/WRO-2026-RoboMission-Technical-Summary.docx"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="flex items-center p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-md transition-all group"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="mr-4 text-slate-400 group-hover:text-blue-500"
                        >
                            <svg
                                width="24"
                                height="24"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                ><path
                                    d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"
                                ></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"
                                ></polyline><line
                                    x1="12"
                                    y1="18"
                                    x2="12"
                                    y2="12"></line><line
                                    x1="9"
                                    y1="15"
                                    x2="15"
                                    y2="15"></line></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold mb-1 text-slate-900">
                                Technical Summary
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
                                ハードウェア仕様とコントローラー制限。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA -->
            <div class="text-center pt-12 pb-24">
                <a
                    href="/#contact"
                    class="inline-block bg-slate-900 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors"
                >
                    RoboMission にエントリーする
                </a>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>
</Layout>
